import Image from 'next/image';
import Accordion from "@components/Accordion";
import Link from "next/link";

This is a website for a fictional convention centre that serves as supplementary material for the <Link href='sit'>SIT</Link> project.

I worked together with a team of designers to create this site over a few weeks. Besides developing the front-end using JavaScript and CSS, I also created the [3D virtual tour](https://www.didasko-online.com/Orana/virtualroom.php#2) plugin using the Three.js library and Blender.  

Check out the live site [here](https://www.didasko-online.com/Orana/facilities.php).
